messages.ssml: <speak>Do you mean <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub>? The World Health Organization announced a name for the disease that is causing the 2019 novel coronavirus outbreak, which was first identified in Wuhan, China. The name of this disease is coronavirus disease 2019, abbreviated as <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub>. In <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub>, <sub alias="C O">‘CO’</sub> stands for ‘corona,’ <sub alias="V I">‘VI’</sub> for ‘virus,’ and ‘D’ for disease.</speak>
